reviewText: I got this movie because of Rene Bond and Suzanne Fields in a hardcore story.  This movie is only an hour long and has little hardcore action.  The picture quality is not very good and in some places audio does not exist.  Most of the action is softcore and rather disjointed so the story is hard to understand-especially the end.  I can't recommend this unless you are a huge fan of Rene Bond before her implants.
